!!! 5
%html
  %head
    %meta{content: 'text/html; charset=UTF-8', :'http-equiv' => 'Content-Type'}
  %body
    %p
      = "Hi #{@user.user_name},"
      %br
      We would like to inform you that the book you have checked out,
      %b
        = @book.title
      , is overdue. Because of this, you have recieved a strike. You
      currently have
      %b
        = @user.strikes.count
        strikes.
      If you don't return this book by
      %b
        = @checkout.due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y')
      you will recieve another strike.
      %br
      \- The Society of Software Engineers
